review_data.title: Hidden gem in Zurich‘s old town
review_data.content: We found this bakery by recommendation, tried the amaretti morbidi and oh my - were they delicious. Soft inside, rich in flavour, just perfect.

review_data.title: History & food
review_data.content: Excellent pastries, snacks, chocolates, everything! A 400yr old bakery in Old Town? Yes, please! Went here a few times while in Zurich.
